450f4d254a69?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/quotesninja/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Quotes Ninja <small>(quotesninja)</small></a> on <span class=\"review-date\">March 27, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Google WooCommerce plug-in helped me to integrate my store with Google services which helped me to boost visibility also helped for tracking performance and simplifying advertising.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great Support</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/cyberrick/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9837cd3fcf6d945971b3aa28b92a8efd5787ed767a5e51445a691a84a5268de9?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9837cd3fcf6d945971b3aa28b92a8efd5787ed767a5e51445a691a84a5268de9?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/cyberrick/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">cyberrick</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">March 27, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Works very well but had a couple of issues with the cache needing to be cleared first and make sure the browser will accept cookies before configuring.  The support was top notch!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Support was excellent</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/omardesko/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8d8512a94b123b2a71f0a4b05eca505ad7aa53c9b584d4a6351c92d215d006e7?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8d8512a94b123b2a71f0a4b05eca505ad7aa53c9b584d4a6351c92d215d006e7?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/omardesko/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">omardesko</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">March 26, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Hi, I receive a good support to fix a problem i had with a plug-in admin variations.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Thanks</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Очень хороший плагин</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/eugenk/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/51bdbcbbc4e5207c78a6f38d5049053f60b41316961c2bf05522e3b4aa937763?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/51bdbcbbc4e5207c78a6f38d5049053f60b41316961c2bf05522e3b4aa937763?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/eugenk/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">eugenk</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">March 26, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Very good plugin for e-commerce</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">cannot customize and stock templates are shocking</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ryanduncan/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/22cd6d5f6f94ed4cf90e5209414f48ea21b2093f4593c929179598be2163a60e?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/22cd6d5f6f94ed4cf90e5209414f48ea21b2093f4593c929179598be2163a60e?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ryanduncan/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">ryanduncan</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">March 25, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I am shocked at how many people rate this plugin so highly as you cannot customize it at all.<br />The amount of plugins i have tried to get around this is beyond frustrating and for that reason alone I cannot recommend this plugin whatsoever.<br />Either people have built shocking online stores or I am missing something as the my account form template does NOT even allow for a business name, SO the only client they allow you to deal with is a private person, so gear up for small business only!! help this make sense to me....<br />Nothing works with this plugin and there is zero customizing so this is a shocking plugin that I haven\'t even been able to utilize as I cannot do anything with it.<br />Anyone know what can edit their templates maybe ill change this opinion but for now im off to try other alternatives such as ecommerce as I hear that rates highly. STAY AWAY and save yourself hours upon hours of frustration.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Very good support</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/marcobutz/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ea2509328efc52cf781b1bb7f02377141f943c9c0fe19f16f86e3fb7a22fd7d6?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ea2509328efc52cf781b1bb7f02377141f943c9c0fe19f16f86e3fb7a22fd7d6?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/marcobutz/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">marcobutz</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">March 24, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I am absolutely satisfied with the support in terms of: </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>responsivness</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>problem solution</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>eager to help </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Thank you very much all you guys.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Best Marco</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">PRECIO ENVIOS</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/1micoruna/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8e5793f6aeb3a3ac6d5deb4493c331855bea585d954e5b37cc8bbc37e18a8560?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8e5793f6aeb3a3ac6d5deb4493c331855bea585d954e5b37cc8bbc37e18a8560?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/1micoruna/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">1micoruna</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">March 23, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Increible la rapidez y buenisima.resolución de mis dudas. Gracias</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Awesome Plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mosesmedh/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/3a88fceb98a2db4faa27116de34d476212995427252b132037d90bc56e66baa3?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/3a88fceb98a2db4faa27116de34d476212995427252b132037d90bc56e66baa3?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mosesmedh/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Moses M. (woo-hc) <small>(mosesmedh)</small></a> on <span class=\"review-date\">March 20, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The plugin is easy to customize and support is swift from the community.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Good overall - lacking some key basics</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/zdriver/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/0ad0cf1466c0a3a9004844f5dc1ac306aa7c8568bacc448b20cd4d159f40c562?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/0ad0cf1466c0a3a9004844f5dc1ac306aa7c8568bacc448b20cd4d159f40c562?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/zdriver/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">zdriver</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">March 20, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Having moved from shopify, woo delivers great freedom. That said it also lacks some basic features you would expect from a mature product. Much of this is around post purchase order management.<br />Creating new orders for an existing client - it doesnt always grab their billing and shipping details which is annoying - never had that issue with shopify. Also editing orders is annoying how it extracts tax component so you need to guess total amount when editing an order if a client wants to change anything. Also if you need to add any products or make a change that needs additional payment, woo is unable to send a payment link along with order update email. Again shopify does this out of the box with ease. and lastly plugins - a necessary evil - each plugin adds a slow down to admin, which has now slowed basic product and order changes right down to a click and wait experience. Again this impact is not seen with shopify, so woo needs to implement standards or a structure that will eliminate this. It does sadden me as I see woo as a superior product, but shopify is pulling away in admin functionality.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:146:\"Everything you need to launch an online store in days and keep it growing for years. From your first sale to millions in revenue, Woo is with you.\";s:13:\"download_link\";s:60:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/woocommerce.9.7.1.zip\";s:14:\"upgrade_notice\";a:0:{}s:11:\"screenshots\";a:6:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:64:\"https://ps.w.org/woocommerce/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=3234504\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:64:\"https://ps.w.org/woocommerce/assets/screenshot-2.png?rev=3234504\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:64:\"https:/