he best ex\";s:16:\"description_html\";s:17411:\"<table>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://thimpress.com/log/charitix-nonprofit-charity-changelog/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://updates.thimpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/top-changelog.jpg\" alt=\"Charitix - Nonprofit Charity WordPress Theme - 1\" /></a> </td>\n<td><a href=\"https://docspress.thimpress.com/charity-wp/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://updates.thimpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/top-docs.jpg\" alt=\"Charitix - Nonprofit Charity WordPress Theme - 2\" /></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"https://thimpress.com/how-to-get-help-from-the-thimpress-support/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://updates.thimpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/top-support.jpg\" alt=\"Charitix - Nonprofit Charity WordPress Theme - 3\" /></a></td>\n</tr> \n</table>\n\n<p><strong>Charity WordPress Theme &#8211; Charity WP</strong> is perfectly built for charity, nonprofit, non-governmental organization (NGO), donation and fundraising campaign with outstanding and amazing features.</p>\n\n	<p><img src=\"https://updates.thimpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/charity2018-item-description.png\" alt=\"Charity Wordpress Theme - Charity WP\" /></p>\n\n\n<h2 id=\"item-description__complete-charity-wordpress-theme\">Complete Charity WordPress Theme</h2>\n\n<p>With many years of experience in WordPress themes &#38; plugins developing, a lot of time is invested to make Charity WP including research features and optimize UI/UX. This theme has all necessary features for a Charity site: create campaigns/projects/causes, donation system, non-profit events, fund raising, crowdfunding campaigns for cause or charity group/organization, call for volunteers, vision and mission page, and many more. These features are built with super friendly UX which offer you the best experience ever of a complete Charity WordPress website.</p>\n\n<p>\n<a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/charity-wordpress-theme-charity-wp/15593989#item-description__6-c