 2.0 - 8\" /> <img src=\"https://updates.thimpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/tf-desc5.png\" alt=\"Classy - Minimal Multipurpose Shopify Theme OS 2.0 - 9\" /> <img src=\"https://updates.thimpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/tf-desc6.png\" alt=\"Classy - Minimal Multipurpose Shopify Theme OS 2.0 - 10\" /> <img src=\"https://updates.thimpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/tf-desc7.png\" alt=\"Classy - Minimal Multipurpose Shopify Theme OS 2.0 - 11\" /> <img src=\"https://updates.thimpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/tf-desc8.png\" alt=\"Classy - Minimal Multipurpose Shopify Theme OS 2.0 - 12\" /> <img src=\"https://updates.thimpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/tf-desc9.png\" alt=\"Classy - Minimal Multipurpose Shopify Theme OS 2.0 - 13\" /> <img src=\"https://updates.thimpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/tf-desc10.png\" alt=\"Classy - Minimal Multipurpose Shopify Theme OS 2.0 - 14\" /> <img src=\"https://updates.thimpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/tf-desc11.png\" alt=\"Classy - Minimal Multipurpose Shopify Theme OS 2.0 - 15\" /> <img src=\"https://updates.thimpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/tf-desc12.png\" alt=\"Classy - Minimal Multipurpose Shopify Theme OS 2.0 - 16\" /></p>\n<h2 id=\"item-description__features\">Features:</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Easy to Import Demo Config (One-Click)</li>\n<li>Social Share Features</li>\n<li>Multi-purpose Designs</li>\n<li>Fast Loading, Optimized for mobile &#38; Better SEO</li>\n<li>Responsive Design, Mobile Optimized &#38; Incredible UI/UX</li>\n<li>Fully Responsive (Tested on Multiple Devices)</li>\n<li>Modern &#38; Clean Design</li>\n<li>Built with CSS 3 + HTML 5, Tailwind</li>\n<li>Google Web Fonts Integration, Support ShopifyΓÇÖs Font Picker, Custom font</li>\n<li>40+ Stunning Homepage Layouts</li>\n<li>10+ Layouts Options for Category Page</li>\n<li>19+ Layouts Options for Product Page</li>\n<li>04+ Layouts Options for Tab Product</li>\n<li>05+ Layouts for product description</li>\n<li>06+ Blog page layouts</li>\n<li>Multiple Headers, Footers</li>\n<li>Custom header &#38; footer for special page</li>\n<li>External &#38; Affiliate Product</li>\n<li>Cart Modal/Cart Drawer/Cart Ajax/Cart Page</li>\n<li>Order Note/Quickly Add A Coupon/Estimate Shipping</li>\n<li>Numerous Custom Pages: Lookbook, FAQs, Contact Us, Portfolio, About us, Contact us, 404, Shop Instagram</li>\n<li>Advanced Mega menu layouts</li>\n<li>GRID &#38; LIST Mode</li>\n<li>Product Reviews (App)</li>\n<li>Zoom Magnifier Support</li>\n<li>Ajax Product Filter Support</li>\n<li>Support multi language and multi currency</li>\n<li>Sticky Header</li>\n<li>Quick Shop</li>\n<li>Ajax Layered Navigation</li>\n<li>Ajax Live Search</li>\n<li>One Click Checkout</li>\n<li>Advanced Size Chart (MaxSale app)</li>\n<li>Custom Product Tabs</li>\n<li>Login &#38; Registration page</li>\n<li>GDPR Cookie Popup (App)</li>\n<li>Sticky Add to Cart</li>\n<li>Lookbook Module</li>\n<li>Automatic Image resize</li>\n<li>Ajax Infinite Scroll module + Ajax Load More + Pagination/ Product Count</li>\n<li>Builder Sections on All page</li>\n<li>Product Image Swap/ Advanced Product Swatches</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong><i> ** Please note:</i>&lt;/strong &gt;<i> Images used and included in this theme are for demo purpose only, NON-COMMERCE PURPOSE. They are not a part of the theme and are NOT included in the final purchase files.</i> </strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://thimpress.com/log/classy-minimal-multipurpose-shopify-theme-changelog/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://thimpress.com/envato/changelogs.jpg\" alt=\"Education WordPress Theme Changelog\" /></a></p>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://help.thimpress.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://thimpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/tf-support.png\" alt=\"Classy - Minimal Multipurpose Shopify Theme OS 2.0 - 17\" /></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"https://docs.thimpress.com/classy-2-0\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://thimpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/tf-document.png\" alt=\"Classy - Minimal Multipurpose Shopify Theme OS 2.0 - 18\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<h4 id=\"item-description__changelogs\">CHANGELOGS</h4>\n<p><strong>Version 2.1.5 &#8211; 26-Apr-2024</strong></p>\n<pre>Added option to display topbar on mobile.\nIncluded language and currency selector in mobile menu.\nFixed issue with shipping estimate feature not functioning.</pre>\n\n<p><strong>Version 2.1.4 &#8211; 03-Apr-2024</strong></p>\n<pre>Added the ability to select color schemes for individual blocks within section slides.\nIntroduced the option to upload images specifically for mobile devices within section slides.\n</pre>\n\n<p><strong>Version 2.1.3 &#8211; 11-Mar-2024</strong></p>\n<pre>Added option to enable/disable pre-order feature.\nFixed issue with duplicate products on collection pages in loadmore mode.\n</pre>\n<p><strong>Version 2.1.2 &#8211; 24-Feb-2024</strong></p>\n<pre>Fix: Resolved issue with inability to disable gift wrap in the cart page.\nNew: Added option to hide product count display on collections page.\n</pre>\n\n<p><strong>Version 2.1.1 &#8211; 24-January-2024</strong></p>\n<pre>Integrated \"Air Reviews\" app into the theme.\nRemoved border from the \"Trust Badge\" block on the product detail page.\nReduced font thickness of the product title on the product detail page.\nAdded a size guide block in image format to the product detail page.\n</pre> \n<p><strong>Version 2.1 &#8211; 16-January-2024</strong></p>\n<pre>Modified: Changed the content option of the slider to \"Richtext\" format.\nFixed: Added margin-bottom to blog tags for proper spacing.\nImplemented minor changes to improve user interface and experience\n</pre>\n\n<p><strong>Version 2.0.9 &#8211; 5-January-2024</strong></p>\n<pre>Updated brand recognition.\nFixed featured image display for product items with no variant images.\n</pre>\n<p><strong>Version 2.0.8 &#8211; 11-December-2023</strong></p>\n<pre>Added: New layout for \"popup newsletter\" with a focus on image-only presentation.\nFixed: Addressed issue with price update functionality for variants when the price is a decimal number. Clicking on variants will now correctly update the displayed price.\n</pre>\n<p><strong>Version 2.0.7 &#8211; 06-December-2023</strong></p>\n<pre>Fixed social share image meta tag issue.\nUpdated typography for heading tags.\nAdded \"Custom class\" option for single link menu block.\n</pre>\n<p><strong>Version 2.0.6 &#8211; 23-November-2023</strong></p>\n<pre>New Home:  Fashion\nNew Function: Ask a Question\nNew Function: Pre-order\n</pre>\n<p><strong>Version 2.0.5 &#8211; 14-November-2023</strong></p>\n<pre>New: Added new homepage Electro\nNew: Added new homepage Fullwidth\n</pre>\n<p><strong>Version 2.0.4 &#8211; 7-November-2023</strong></p>\n<pre>Fix: Addressed the problem with shipping estimates not working when opening the AJAX cart. Now, shipping estimates function accurately and display the correct information for your customers \nNew: Added a new home page: Classic, featuring a sleek and minimalist design for a unique shopping experience.</pre>\n<p><strong>Version 2.0.3 &#8211; 31-October-2023</strong></p>\n<pre>Fix: Fixed several issues with the right-to-left interface.\nNew: Introducing a feature for external/affiliate products.\nNew: Added a new FAQ page.\n</pre>\n<p><strong>Version 2.0.2 &#8211; 26-October-2023</strong></p>\n<pre>New: Added Homepage Marketplace \nFix: Fixed some minor bugs.</pre>\n<p><strong>Version 2.0.1 &#8211; 24-October-2023</strong></p>\n<pre>+ Upsell Bundle:\nIntroducing the \"Upsell Bundle\" feature, a powerful tool to boost your sales. With this feature, you can now create and promote product bundles, encourage customers to purchase related items together. Increase your average order value and offer your customers a more convenient shopping experience.\n+ Right to Left (RTL) Support:\nWe\'re thrilled to announce full Right to Left (RTL) language support in our application. Now, you can cater to a wider audience by providing a seamless user experience for languages such as Arabic, Hebrew, and Persian. Your website or application will automatically adapt to RTL content, making it more inclusive and accessible.\n+ Menu Labeling:\nEnhance the usability of your website or application with our new \"Menu Labeling\" feature. You can now easily label your menus, make navigation more intuitive for your users. Adding labels to menus helps visitors quickly locate the sections or categories they\'re interested in, results are shown in a smoother and more user-friendly experience.\n+ Short Descriptions for Product Details:\nWe\'ve added the ability to include short descriptions in your product details. This feature provides concise and informative snippets about your products, gives customers a quick overview of key features and benefits. Improve the shopping experience by providing essential information at a glance.\n</pre>\n<p><strong>Version 2.0.0 &#8211; 14-October-2023</strong></p>\n<pre>Upgraded to Version 2.0 with numerous enhancements, making it faster and more user-friendly.\nUpdated UI/UX with a distinctive and minimalist style.\nAdded the \"Custom Variant Color\" feature for greater flexibility.\nOptimized website loading speed.\nEnhanced the admin interface for improved usability.</pre>\n<p><a href=\"https://thimpress.com/log/classy-minimal-multipurpose-shopify-theme-changelog/\" rel=\"nofollow\">See All changelogs</a></p>\";s:4:\"site\";s:15:\"themeforest.net\";s:14:\"classification\";s:25:\"ecommerce/shopify/fashion\";s:18:\"classification_url\";s:58:\"https://themeforest.net/category/ecommerce/shopify/fashion\";s:11:\"price_cents\";i:1900;s:15:\"number_of_sales\";i:539;s:15:\"author_username\";s:9:\"ThimPress\";s:10:\"author_url\";s:38:\"https://themeforest.net/user/ThimPress\";s:12:\"author_image\";s:50:\"https://0.s3.envato.com/files/166436140/icon-1.png\";s:3:\"url\";s:82:\"https://themeforest.net/item/storepify-minimal-multipurpose-shopify-theme/40668860\";s:7:\"summary\";s:177: