ploads/2022/03/top-support.jpg\" alt=\"Course Builder - Online Course WordPress Theme - 3\" /></a></td>\n</tr> \n</table>\n\n	<p><a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/education-wordpress-theme-education-wp/14058034\"><img src=\"https://updates.thimpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/eduma-theme.png\" alt=\"Course Builder - Online Course WordPress Theme - 4\" /></a></p>\n\n\n<p><strong>The Course Builder WordPress Theme</strong> is a high quality LMS (Learning Management System) theme for Corporate, Multisite Business, Group, Company&#8230; to create training websites for employees. The flexibility and power of Course Builder can help you easily create beautiful online courses, share your knowledge to your employees. With <strong>Course Builder WordPress Theme</strong>, you will have a perfect LMS for training website built from <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/learnpress/\" rel=\"nofollow\">LearnPress &#8211; 1# LMS WordPress Plugin. </a></p>\n<p><strong>The Course Builder WordPress Theme</strong> with LSM made exclusively for you &#8211; <strong>Course Builder</strong></p>\n<ul><li>Share your knowledge and inspire your employees.</li>\n<li>Improve your employees&#8217; skills with beautiful online courses.</li>\n<li>Train your employees online with video and text lesson content, quizzes, multiple question types, certificate, comment system, email notification, online webinar,&#8230;.</li>\n<li>An online corporate training website which is easy to implement, easy to use and dose not take much of your time.</li>\n</ul>\n<img src=\"https://updates.thimpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Sc_2.jpg\" alt=\"Course Builder - Online Course WordPress Theme - 5\" />\n<a href=\"http://coursebuilder.thimpress.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://updates.thimpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/highlight-coursebuilder.png\" alt=\"Course Builder - Online Course WordPress Theme - 6\" /></a>\n\n	<p><strong>Course Builder WordPress Theme features:</strong></p>\n\n\n	